Zatupki Guessing Game

How well do you know your friends?

Welcome to the CliftonStrengths guessing game! Test your knowledge of your friends' top strengths and bottom traits.

How to Play:

  • Drag traits from the bank to each person's slots
  • Stage 1: Guess everyone's Top 5 Strengths
  • Stage 2: Guess everyone's Bottom 5 Traits
  • Use hints strategically - they cost points!
  • Earn +20 pts for correct traits, +10 pts for correct domains

Scoring System

+20 pts Correct trait placement

-5 pts Using Hint 2 (trait reveal)
